entry.title: CompositionalIT/fparsec-chess-pgn
entry.summary:
Using FParsec to parse Portable Game Notation (PGN) for Chess

FParsecChess

An example repo showing how to use FParsec to make a simple parser in F# for Portable Game Notation for Chess.

To run the tests:

dotnet tool restore
dotnet watch run --project tests
